(secondQuint)Study to Evaluate Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics of Minocin (Minocycline) for Injection in Healthy Adults.

 The purpose of this study is to collect safety, tolerability, and PK data on ascending dose regimens of Minocin(R) (minocycline) for Injection.

 The safety, tolerability, and PK data will support the compound as a potential clinical candidate in Europe and allow recommendations of dose levels to be used in future Phase 2/3 studies.

